    "verse_groups": 5,
    "verse_lines": 34,
    "description": "The XML has one authorial preface, one table of contents, and 127 body DIV1 sections (129 DIV1 elements total). Among the 127 body sections, 125 are prose-only and two contain both prose and verse; the authorial preface contains three further verse groups. Counts describe the encoding, not a critical taxonomy of the medieval work.",
